<P>
* This is finals week at UC San Diego, so Primal Scream Therapy is sanctioned. 
</P>
<P>
For five minutes each night (starting at 9:55 p.m.) upwards of 1,000 students 
at Muir College scream their heads off to relieve stress. Then back to the 
books. 
</P>
