COUNTY -- POLITICS; POLITICAL CAMPAIGNS; LOS ANGELES COUNTY -- ELECTIONS -- 
1990; LOS ANGELES COUNTY -- TRANSPORTATION; TRANSIT SYSTEMS -- LOS ANGELES 
COUNTY; LOS ANGELES COUNTY -- FINANCES 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
