transport the 75-ton excavator from Sacramento to San Juan Capistrano. ; Photo, 
(Ventura County Edition) Highway officials confer under the damaged transition 
from the northbound Hollywood Freeway to the northbound Golden State Freeway 
after it was closed. JOEL P. LUGAVERE / Los Angeles Times; Photo, (Ventura 
County Edition) An officer's car blocks freeway lanes in the San Fernando 
Valley. The 2:30 p.m. accident tied up commuter traffic for hours. 
</P>
