CITYPHOTOGRAPHERS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA120590-0113 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 317954 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
December 5, 1990, Wednesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
